[center][img]https://github.com/Majrusz/MinecraftCommon/blob/main/Accessories/logo.png?raw=true[/img]

[size=14px]This [b]forge[/b] modification adds new special accessories to make certain aspects of the game more enjoyable.
A detailed description of all accessories can be found on the [url=https://majruszs-accessories.fandom.com/wiki/Majrusz%27s_Accessories_Wiki]Wiki[/url].[/size]
[style size=14px color=#f00]This mod requires a [url=/mod/majrusz-library/][color=#f00]Majrusz Library[/color][/url][/style][style size=14px color=#f00] to work![/style]

[img]https://github.com/Majrusz/MinecraftCommon/blob/main/Accessories/stuff.png?raw=true[/img]

[style b size=18px]Efficiency Bonus[/style]
[size=14px]All accessories have randomized efficiency bonus which makes them more or less useful.
Description is generated dynamically to show you the final value with efficiency included.[/size]
[img]https://github.com/Majrusz/MinecraftCommon/blob/main/Accessories/bonus.png?raw=true[/img]

[style b size=18px]Recycling[/style]
[size=14px]All redundant duplicates can be sold in certain villager's trade.[/size]
[img]https://github.com/Majrusz/MinecraftCommon/blob/main/Accessories/trades.png?raw=true[/img]

[style b size=18px]Increasing efficiency bonus[/style]
[size=14px]Multiple accessories of the same type can be combined to reroll the efficiency bonus.[/size]
[img]https://github.com/Majrusz/MinecraftCommon/blob/main/Accessories/crafting.png?raw=true[/img]

[style b size=18px]Combining different accessories[/style]
[size=14px]It is possible to combine certain accessories to get a new accessory with all bonuses included.
Some of the bonuses are even stronger in the new accessory![/size]
[img]https://github.com/Majrusz/MinecraftCommon/blob/main/Accessories/crafting2.png?raw=true[/img]

[style b size=18px]How to activate the accessory?[/style]
[size=14px]If you have [url=https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/curios][b]Curios API[/b][/url] installed then accessories work when placed in a new [b]Pocket[/b] slot.
Otherwise, they work only when held in the second hand.[/size]

